  <p><a href="/Support/AdoptSpecies/AnimalInfo/AsianEleph/" class="AttentionBody">Adopt</a> an Asian Elephant!</p>
  <p><img src="/admin/images/icons/icon_pdf.gif" width="15" height="11" /><a href="/Publications/PressMaterials/PressKit/ElephantTrails/overview.pdf" target="pdf">Overview of the new Elephant Community Center</a></p>
